quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  17,1,"Senaare wondani oon do∆īnu…óo Jeyaa…óo makko on jehma, iwde ta juulirde hormante haa ka juulirde wo…ó…óitiinde, nden nde min mbarkini banŇče mun,fii yo min kollu mo immorde e aayeeje amen. Pellet, Ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ji‚Äôoowo."
  17,2,"Min njnniino Muusaa deftere nden, men mba…ói nde peewal, wonan'de …ďi…ó…ďe Israa‚Äôiila …ďen, won'de : "Wata on njogito ga Am kooloraa…óo"."
  17,3,"[Ko onon yo] …ďi…ó…ďe …ďe …ďe min mba…ó…óinnoo wonnudude e Nuuhu.Pellet, o laatino jeyaa…óo yettoowo."
  17,4,"Min mbahyinino e …ďi…ó…ďe Israa‚Äôiila …ďe to deftere [won'de] : "On mbonnayat ta leydi laabi …ói…ói, on townitoyto kadi townitaare mawnnde"."
  17,5,"Si fodoore gootel e …óin …ói…ói arii, min ngurta e mon jiyaa…ďe Amen, mar…ďe doole tii…ó…óe, …ďe njiloo hakkunde galleeji …ói. ∆äuum wonii fodoore huuwoyteende =golloteende."
  17,6,"Refti min nduttitanani on n on doole …óen e hoore ma…ď…ďe; min ∆Āeydi on jaw…óe e …ďi…ó…ďe,min mba…óa on gorol …ďurngol heewde."
  17,7,"Si on mo∆ī∆īinii, ko ko'e mon mo∆ī∆īinan…óon ; si on mbonnii kadi, ko ko‚Äôe mon [bonnann…óon]. Si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, ko fii yo …ďe hoynu j'eece mon …óen, e fii yo no …ďe naatiraa ka juulirde wano …ďe naatirnoo e mayre ka laawol adanol, e fii yo …ďe muncu yeru woo ko …ďe townani muncudee."